Package de.cuioss.test.valueobjects.generator

Class JavaTypesGenerator<T>

java.lang.Object
de.cuioss.test.valueobjects.generator.JavaTypesGenerator<T>
Type Parameters:
T - identifying the type to be generated
public final class JavaTypesGenerator<T> extends Object
Factory for creating instances PropertyMetadata for standard java-types and primitives.

Usually it is used with the metadata(String) method that will create concrete instances. In case you want to to further configure the result you can access the corresponding builder with metadataBuilder(String)

Author:
Oliver Wolff
